data.description: Welcome HOME! This stunning 4-bedrrom home exudes elegance at every turn. As you step inside, you are greeted by an exquisite open concept design seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. This creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere perfect for entertaining guests. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace that serves as the focal point adding warmth and charm to the room. A study and a library complete the main floor living giving you the opportunity to create a possible 5th bedroom. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary offering an en suite and gorgeous tray ceiling.  The remaining 3 bedrooms are equally impressive. Additional features: Large loft, a massive finished basement with full bath, and a large corner lot.
